      <title>OpenAI、亚马逊、谷歌同意在 2024 年选举中打击人工智能滥用行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/openai-amazon-google-agree-to-fight-ai-abuse-in-2024-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OpenAI、亚马逊、谷歌和人工智能技术领域的其他 17 个主要参与者组成了一个联盟，试图阻止人工智能在即将到来的全球选举中被用来欺骗选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/openai-amazon-google-agree-to-fight-ai-abuse-in-2024-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 17:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
