    <item>
      <title>视频游戏裁员背后的原因是什么？玩家坚持旧的最爱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/behind-the-video-game-layoffs-players-love-of-old-favorites</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着视频游戏玩家越来越多地沉迷于他们多年来沉迷的游戏，这个价值 1,840 亿美元的行业的领导者正在裁员数千人，并取消风险较高的项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/behind-the-video-game-layoffs-players-love-of-old-favorites</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2023年德国对华直接投资将创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/german-direct-investment-in-china-rose-to-record-in-2023</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，德国企业对华直接投资达到创纪录的近 120 亿欧元（130 亿美元），显示出德国企业在世界第二大经济体中扩张的渴望，尽管欧盟出于安全考虑加强了对这些投资的审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/german-direct-investment-in-china-rose-to-record-in-2023</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 16:32:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在业界反对下，欧盟未能通过零工规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/eu-fails-to-pass-rules-on-gig-workers-amid-industry-opposition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟多年来在零工经济中监管工人权利的努力未能在周五获得成员国足够的投票，导致该行业许多人反对的立法脱轨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/eu-fails-to-pass-rules-on-gig-workers-amid-industry-opposition</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 15:26:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
